BN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-3-447-01603-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-3-447-01603-2">978-3-447-01603-2</a>, pp. 134â135;<br /><a href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Rig_Veda/Mandala_1/Hymn_164" class="extiw" title="s:The Rig Veda/Mandala 1/Hymn 164">Rigveda Book 1, Hymn 164</a> Wikisource</span>
